  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3675060/extras/9098be0c741ac8483c7970822d9f7a8f.avif?t=1749697115\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3675060/extras_big/9098be0c741ac8483c7970822d9f7a8f.avif?t=1749697115 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"Goblin Gnome Horn\"</strong> is <strong>a casual 2D side-scrolling action game.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players control a small goblin named \"Nekbi\" and aim to defeat the Demon King by collecting acorns through various mini-games such as \"chopping firewood\" and \"cleaning the toilet.\"</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Contents</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Labor\" - Simple mini-games such as only clicking or only moving up, down, left and right. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Battle\" - Side-scrolling action battles against the demon king.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play Time</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is estimated that it will take about 2 hours to complete. It can be enjoyed casually.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Labor (Mini-game)</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3675060/extras/1d403b09630d79ac3b10ba2fd5062073.poster.avif?t=1749697115\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3675060/extras/1d403b09630d79ac3b10ba2fd5062073.webm?t=1749697115\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3675060/extras/1d403b09630d79ac3b10ba2fd5062073.mp4?t=1749697115\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・There are a total of 6 types of labor (mini-games).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・You can earn acorns depending on how well you do in the mini-games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・If you get an S rank in a mini-game, you'll get a lot of acorns and new mini-games will be unlocked. Aim to get an S rank.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Trading (shop)</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3675060/extras/ec7c6ff557647f53b6604398f3f76fc0.avif?t=1749697115\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3675060/extras_big/ec7c6ff557647f53b6604398f3f76fc0.avif?t=1749697115 width=800 height=446 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・You can purchase equipment and skills with acorns.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・You'll need a lot of acorns to purchase powerful equipment, so play the mini-game multiple times.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Battle</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3675060/extras/d2de31bacb222e8de4311fdd169ba0e2.poster.avif?t=1749697115\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3675060/extras/d2de31bacb222e8de4311fdd169ba0e2.webm?t=1749697115\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3675060/extras/d2de31bacb222e8de4311fdd169ba0e2.mp4?t=1749697115\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・The only enemy is the Demon King. He is in the next room, so you can challenge him anytime and as many times as you like.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・The game is cleared when you defeat the Demon King.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Left click to attack, right click to parry.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・You can recover stamina by consuming acorns.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>・It's up to you whether you defeat the Demon King by working hard and using strong equipment, or by using your own strength.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▶︎Text can be switched between Japanese and English.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▶︎Gameplay can be streamed.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3675060/extras/9098be0c741ac8483c7970822d9f7a8f.avif?t=1749697115\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3675060/extras_big/9098be0c741ac8483c7970822d9f7a8f.avif?t=1749697115 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"Goblin Gnome Horn\"</strong> is <strong>a casual 2D side-scrolling action game.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players control a small goblin named \"Nekbi\" and aim to defeat the Demon King by collecting acorns through various mini-games such as \"chopping firewood\" and \"cleaning the toilet.\"</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Contents</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Labor\" - Simple mini-games such as only clicking or only moving up, down, left and right. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Battle\" - Side-scrolling action battles against the demon king.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play Time</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is estimated that it will take about 2 hours to complete. It can be enjoyed casually.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Labor (Mini-game)</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3675060/extras/1d403b09630d79ac3b10ba2fd5062073.poster.avif?t=1749697115\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3675060/extras/1d403b09630d79ac3b10ba2fd5062073.webm?t=1749697115\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3675060/extras/1d403b09630d79ac3b10ba2fd5062073.mp4?t=1749697115\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・There are a total of 6 types of labor (mini-games).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・You can earn acorns depending on how well you do in the mini-games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・If you get an S rank in a mini-game, you'll get a lot of acorns and new mini-games will be unlocked. Aim to get an S rank.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Trading (shop)</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3675060/extras/ec7c6ff557647f53b6604398f3f76fc0.avif?t=1749697115\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3675060/extras_big/ec7c6ff557647f53b6604398f3f76fc0.avif?t=1749697115 width=800 height=446 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・You can purchase equipment and skills with acorns.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・You'll need a lot of acorns to purchase powerful equipment, so play the mini-game multiple times.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Battle</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3675060/extras/d2de31bacb222e8de4311fdd169ba0e2.poster.avif?t=1749697115\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3675060/extras/d2de31bacb222e8de4311fdd169ba0e2.webm?t=1749697115\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3675060/extras/d2de31bacb222e8de4311fdd169ba0e2.mp4?t=1749697115\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・The only enemy is the Demon King. He is in the next room, so you can challenge him anytime and as many times as you like.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・The game is cleared when you defeat the Demon King.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Left click to attack, right click to parry.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・You can recover stamina by consuming acorns.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>・It's up to you whether you defeat the Demon King by working hard and using strong equipment, or by using your own strength.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▶︎Text can be switched between Japanese and English.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▶︎Gameplay can be streamed.</p>",
